''' Bengal-ngî ''' ({{IAST|bāṅlā}} / {{lang|bn|বাংলা}} fe̍t-chá {{IAST|bāṅālī}} / {{lang|bn|বাঙালী}}) su̍k-yî [[Yin-Êu Ngî-hì]] [[Yin-thu Iran Ngî-chhu̍k]] ke [[Yin-thu Arya Ngî-kî]], he [[Bangladesh]] fò [[Yin-thu]] [[Sî Bengal]] lâu [[Tripura]] ke [[kôn-fông ngî-ngièn]], sṳ́-yung ngìn-khiéu yok 2 yi 2 chhiên van-ngìn, he Yin-thu Iran Ngî-chhu̍k chhai [[Hindi-ngî]] chṳ̂-heu thi-ngi thai ngî-ngièn. Bengal-ngî sṳ́-yung chú-yeu fûn-pu yî Bangladesh lâu Yin-thu Sî Bengal tén. Bengal-ngî he 1913-ngièn [[Nobel Vùn-ho̍k-chióng]] fe̍t-tet chá [[Yîn-su̍k Yin-thu]] ke [[Rabindranath Tagore]] ke mû-ngî. 
